<hr />
<p>
<span class="title">Personnel Search For Form 8 Entry </span><br />
     User can search the records by writing Personnel Name,Pass No.,Unit(Select unit from the drop down box),Designation(select designation from the drop down box) and click on the search button.<br />
<br />
<span class="title">GRID (Display): </span> <br />
   Based on search criteria data will display in the form of table. At a time only five (5) records will be displayed. To navigate or look for the next record pagination (the system of numbering pages) will be there. 
<br />
    <span class="title">OK Button and Text Box: </span> 
    <br />If user wants to switch directly to any particular page no, then he can simply enter the page no. in the given text box and click on OK Button.
<br />



 <span class="title">See Rule 61 (1):</span><br />   
 
 
         <span class="title">    Pass No.:</span><br />This will show the pass no. of the record selected by you.  <br />
          <span class="title">   Personnel Name :</span><br /> this will show the Personnel name of the record selected by you.  <br />  
          <span class="title">  File No.: </span><br /> User can write File No. in this text box.  <br />  
           <span class="title">  Date: </span><br /> User can write Date in this text box.  <br />  
         <span class="title">   2.)The detail of Govt.dues which will remain outstanding on the date of retirement of the Govt. servant and which need to be recovered out of the amount of death-cum-retirement gratuity are indicated below :- </span> <br />
         <span class="title">   a.)Balance of house building or conveyance advance:</span><br /> User can write Balance of house building or conveyance advance in this text box.<br />
         <span class="title">   b.)Over payment of pay and allowance including leave salary:</span><br /> User can write Over payment of pay and allowance including leave salary in this text box.<br />
         <span class="title">   c.)Income Tax deductible at source under the Income Tax act[1961](43 of 1961):</span><br /> User can write Income Tax deductible at source under the Income Tax act[1961](43 of 1961) in this text box.<br />
         <span class="title">   d.)Arrears of licence fee for occupation of govt.accomodation:</span><br /> User can write Arrears of licence fee for occupation of govt.accomodation in this text box.<br />
         <span class="title">   e.)Amount of licence fee for the retention of the govt. accomodation for the permissible period of two month beyond the date of retirement:</span><br /> User can write Amount of licence fee for the retention of the govt. accomodation for the permissible period of two month beyond the date of retirement in this text box.<br />
         <span class="title">   f.)Any other assessed dues and the nature there of:</span><br /> User can write Any other assessed dues and the nature there of in this text box.<br />
         <span class="title">   g.)Amount of gratuity to be with held for the adjustment of un-assessed dues if any:</span><br /> User can write Amount of gratuity to be with held for the adjustment of un-assessed dues if any in this text box.<br />
         <span class="title">  Total :</span><br /> User can write Total in this text box.<br />   
 
   <span class="title">Update(Button): </span>
    <br />By clicking on Update button user can Update the data.
<br />
    <span class="title">Back (Button): </span> 
    <br />Clicking on back button user can visit the previous screen.
